### 🌐 Deploying to AWS (S3 + CloudFront)

For full control and scalability:

1. Build your app: `npm run build`
2. Upload `build/` to an S3 bucket.
3. Enable static website hosting in S3.
4. Set up CloudFront for CDN and HTTPS.
5. Configure Route 53 for DNS.

```bash
